#X text 32 139 The [pdluax foo] object loads "foo.pd_luax" at object creation time.;
#X text 32 197 + You can edit "foo.pd_luax" and new [pdluax foo] objects will reflect the changes in the file.;
#X text 32 233 + Good for rapid development/testing cycles.;
#X text 32 255 + Good for live coding.;
#X text 32 276 + No need to restart Pd if you made a little mistake.;
